Blockchain Specialist

https://jobscentral.com.sg/job/blockchain-specialist-jcrwldmau6vyz46w3p?iPath=JRKCVT&utm_campaign=google_jobs_apply&utm_source=google_jobs_apply&utm_medium=organic

LOCATION_TYPE: Singapore

WORK_TYPE: FULL-TIME

ABOUT THE PROJECT:
We are looking to expand our Blockchain development team with highly motivated and self-driven Software Engineer(s) for mid to senior-level positions to be based in Singapore. You will be building out robust, performant and secure applications on distributed, decentralised platforms.

RESPONSIBLITIES :
• Contributing to different phases and cycles of a full product to the production environment

• Help guide and manage the blockchain team to fulfil their project objectives (For Senior Positions)

• Learn, research and break new blockchain protocols in the industry

• Participate in strategic planning to achieve business goals by identifying and prioritising development initiatives and setting timelines for the evaluation, development and deployment of products.

DESIRED SKILLS/ATTRIBUTES/EDUCATION/EXPERIENCE
• At least a Bachelor’s Degree in IT or equivalent 

• Proficient in any one of these: Node.js/Typescript/Python/GoLang

• Design, implementing and maintaining production-grade RESTful APIs.

• At least with 1-3 years of experience with Blockchain platforms and languages such as Ethereum(Web3.js), Solidity Smart contracts, Hyperledger, Corda, HD Wallet Management.

• Production grade hands-on with databases such as MySQL, Postgres, MongoDB, DynamoDB, Firebase etc.

• Experience with cloud infrastructure services such as AWS, GCP etc

• A decent understanding of one or more component-based front-development frameworks, such as React.js or Vue.js;

• Exposure to message queues/brokers such as RabbitMQ, ZMQ or Apache Kafka.

• Highly enthusiastic about blockchain and new technologies in the market;

• Developer background with excellent knowledge about blockchain/crypto, security and data protection methods;

• Experience in a technical leadership role with proven ability to lead teams and delegate responsibilities;

• Excellent communication skills, both verbal and written;

• Experience in the architecture and development of blockchain products;

• Ability to work independently and launch your own initiatives, without the need to be micromanaged;

• Ability to think strategically and critically, implementing new technological solutions seamlessly.
